question.title: Spring Boot Project application.properties file disapeared
question.body:
I have a running Java Spring project that previously contained an application.properties file. Today, when I wanted to update some configuration, I noticed that the file is missing.

  • It’s not in Git history.

  • It doesn’t show up in my IDE (Eclipse).

  • It’s not present in the project directory either.

What could be the possible reasons for this behavior, and how should I go about debugging the issue?
